snippet.title: Super Buckyball Tournament Alpha Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Buckyball Tournament first alpha is launching on August 31st!

Register now available at http://en.sbt.pathea.net and the game pack can be downloaded via either Game Jolt http://bit.ly/2KPZfbl or itch.io http://bit.ly/3245Ftv

For more details about this alpha, join discord https://discord.gg/BAc8gvw

Wishlist us on Steam to get notified when the game is releasing http://bit.ly/2K0905l

Follow us on social media to receive the latest updates about the game:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/SuperBuckyBall
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SuperBuckyballtournament
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/superbuckyballtournament
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SuperBuckyballTourney/
